history.content:
Hi Piazza fam; 

A quick reminder that if you have feedback or concerns about your TA/GSI/UGSI, you should feel free to share them with the faculty of record. Your faculty really do want to know if there is a problem.

If you feel uncomfortable doing that, you are always welcome to talk to any staff member in Student Affairs. We're here to help! 

Take care,

Sarah
